{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7936d0fc1","title":"和陈昌奉的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"085a6d7b58","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"d7936d0fc1"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a77b07c768","type":"title","text":"和陈昌奉的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1"},{"id":"e7aa34b734","type":"paragraph","text":"山东地方很好，根据地很大，新解放了许多县城，很需要十部。到那里要尊重地方，尊重地方干部，尊重新单位的负责人，要和当地干部搞好团结","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1"},{"id":"a9f94362d5","type":"paragraph","text":"学习也好，倒不是为当官，而是为人民多做些事。当然，学习中间也有很多困难，只要你有为人民服务的决心，什么困难都能克服","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1"},{"id":"7843195212","type":"paragraph","text":"指导员也是革命工作嘛！非当上什么官才行吗","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1"},{"id":"89ed8310da","type":"paragraph","text":"想当官的人到共产党这里来就是走错门啦！我们这里还有什么官不官啊！都是一样。我们是为人民服务的，到我们这里发财当然不用说了，想升管也达不到目的","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1"}],"page":{"id":"7ed555c211","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"d7936d0fc1","start":529,"end":529}}}},"__N_SSG":true}